name: 100-year-floodplain-for-south-louisiana-utm-15n-nad83-lra-2005-floodplain
notes: This GIS raster grid data set illustrates FEMA Q3 floodplain data for 34 of 35 parishes in the Louisiana Speaks Regional Plan South Louisiana study area. The data set is a compilation of currently digitized FEMA Q3 data and hand-coded FEMA DFIRM maps for ONLY Zone X (100-Year Floodplain). FEMA floodzone data compiled before updates were made after Hurricane Katrina and Rita.
